#loggr

Experiment in connecting a PyQt GUI to Erlang via 0MQ

See original blog post http://23min.com/2013/03/erlang-to-pyqt-via-0mq/

##Author(s)

* Peter Bruinsma <peter@23min.com>

##License

Public Domain

##Usage

Install Qt5, SIP, PyQt


In the shall, start the Python gui:

		$ cd client
		$ python gui.py

In another shell:

		$ make all
		$ make run

Send text from Erlang to the gui:

		$ logga_server:send(<<"Ponies!">>).


